    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras/f79c3f43e2f4188819515feb39c246c4.avif?t=1772046050\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras_big/f79c3f43e2f4188819515feb39c246c4.avif?t=1772046050 width=800 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>丰满立体的角色</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于Amelia 的世界——她是一名看似文静却内心倔强的普通少女，热爱轮滑与摄影！一心只想回家的她，却突然落入一位沉迷时间旅行的科学家之手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras/c00b9135679867ed7586b0946ecc3b70.avif?t=1772046050\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras_big/c00b9135679867ed7586b0946ecc3b70.avif?t=1772046050 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>剧情驱动的游戏体验</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探究绑架你的时间旅行科学家Ron的故事，揭开他引人入胜的过往！见证Amelia在逃脱过程中，与 Ron之间逐步展开的剧情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras/0e6ddc96e723ae7049aef74d9f34fa1b.avif?t=1772046050\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras_big/0e6ddc96e723ae7049aef74d9f34fa1b.avif?t=1772046050 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>探索解谜 沉浸玩法</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用你的智慧，完成趣味互动谜题，找到逃出房间的方法。休闲风格，让你可以按照自己的想法，自由选择解谜顺序，最终找到回家之路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras/e31201baf757f7278df1919ad13a55e1.avif?t=1772046050\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263090/extras_big/e31201baf757f7278df1919ad13a55e1.avif?t=1772046050 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你，能否成功逃脱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏支持瞬移 / 快速转向操作，或是摇杆移动模式！</p>",
